          <strong> 80+ digital products </strong>
          for top-tier partners.
        </p>

        <p class="about-body a3">
          In my current role, I'm a part of an AI-First team of UX/Product designers in a dynamic
          Fintech environment, I collaborate with cross-functional teams, and ensure our solutions
          are user-centered, intuitive, and aligned with business goals.
        </p>

        <p class="about-body a4">
          Over the past three years, I've had the privilege of training and mentoring 3,000+ UX
          students across multiple regions, actively shaping the next generation of UX leaders.
        </p>
