    <section class="slide slide-ai-definition slide-dark-grid" data-title="AI-first Product Designer" aria-label="AI-first product designer slide">
      <div class="grid-overlay af"></div>

      <div class="ai-def-stage">
        <div class="ai-def-copy-block">
          <h2 class="ai-def-title a1">
            What is An <span class="accent">AI-first</span><br>
            Product Designer Means?
          </h2>

          <p class="ai-def-subtitle a2">
            An AI-first Product Designer is a product designer who treats AI as a core part of both the product and the design process.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-def-cards a3">
          <article class="ai-def-card">
            <div class="ai-def-card-head">
              <p class="ai-def-card-index">01</p>
              <h3 class="ai-def-card-title">AI Product</h3>
              <div class="ai-def-card-rule"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="ai-def-card-text">Design products where AI is part of the user experience itself, like copilots, recommendations, chat interfaces, automation, or predictive workflows.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="ai-def-card">
            <div class="ai-def-card-head">
              <p class="ai-def-card-index">02</p>
              <h3 class="ai-def-card-title">Design Workflow</h3>
              <div class="ai-def-card-rule"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="ai-def-card-text">Design products where AI is part of the user experience itself, like copilots, recommendations, chat interfaces, automation, or predictive workflows.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="ai-def-card">
            <div class="ai-def-card-head">
              <p class="ai-def-card-index">03</p>
              <h3 class="ai-def-card-title">Human Judgment</h3>
              <div class="ai-def-card-rule"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="ai-def-card-text">relying on human judgment for product direction, usability, and quality. <strong style="color:#fff;">NN/g</strong> frames AI as an assistant across design work rather than a replacement for design thinking.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide slide-gaia-intro slide-intro-light light-ui" data-title="GAIA" aria-label="GAIA intro slide">
      <div class="light-grid-bg af"></div>

      <div class="intro-title-block">
        <div class="section-overline a1">
          <div class="section-overline-line"></div>
          <div class="section-overline-text">1st Product GAIA</div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="intro-title a1">GAIA</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="intro-copy-stack">
        <p class="intro-lead a2">GAIA is an eco-tech initiative building AI systems that represent ecosystems inside governance processes.</p>
        <p class="intro-body a3">Its core product, ENVAI, combines ecological data, cultural context, and legal reasoning to create a continuous, auditable, place-based representative for a river or ecosystem.</p>
        <div class="info-grid a4">
