      <aside class="questions-side">
        <div class="questions-side-stack">
          <p class="questions-side-lead a2">If you havenÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¾ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢t been involved in designing an AI product or feature yet, here is a practical step to get started.</p>

          <div class="side-card a3">
            <p class="quote-mark">"</p>
            <h3 class="side-card-title">Take the Initiative</h3>
            <ul class="side-card-list">
              <li>Read up on AI basics, learning about common AI concepts.</li>
              <li>Collaborate with an engineer on a small AI feature project to understand technical constraints.</li>
              <li>Analyze successful AI products. Understand how they explain the AIÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¾ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢s role to users.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="slide slide-ai-workflow light-ui" data-title="AI in Design Workflow" aria-label="AI workflow slide">
      <div class="light-grid-bg af"></div>
      <h2 class="workflow-title a1">Use <span class="accent">AI</span> in design workflow</h2>

      <div class="workflow-credit a2">
        <div class="workflow-credit-avatar">
          <img src="https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/1bb77873-80bf-470a-85cd-f5a74cb51095" alt="">
        </div>
        <p class="workflow-credit-name">Menna Kenawy</p>
        <p class="workflow-credit-role">UI/UX Designer</p>
      </div>

      <div class="workflow-frame a3">
        <img src="https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/0979c6f5-138b-413a-b1b7-1e754848360b" alt="">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide slide-thanks" data-title="Thank You" aria-label="Thank you slide">
      <div class="grid-overlay af"></div>

      <div class="thanks-glow af" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/c05c8c39-097b-449d-bc59-6438ab886f08" alt="">
      </div>

      <div class="thanks-center">
        <h2 class="thanks-title a1">Thank <span class="accent">You</span></h2>

        <div class="thanks-copy a2">
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px;">Feel free to connect with me on LinkedIn.</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 6px;">If you start applying any of the ideas we discussed, and have questions,<br>donÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¾ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢t hesitate to reach out. IÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€ Ã¢â‚¬â„¢ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¡ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¬ÃƒÆ’Ã†â€™Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢ÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¢ÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ã‚Â¬Ãƒâ€¦Ã‚Â¾ÃƒÆ’Ã¢â‚¬Å¡Ãƒâ€šÃ‚Â¢m always happy to support and continue the conversation.</p>
          <p style="margin:0;">Looking forward to seeing what you build.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="speaker-row a3">
          <img
            class="speaker-avatar"
            src="https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/502be2ec-afad-4d0c-8d4c-7b019a423c1c"
            alt=""
            aria-hidden="true"
          >

          <div class="speaker-details">
            <p class="speaker-name">Sayed Abdelaal</p>
            <p class="speaker-role">Product Designer</p>
          </div>

          <div class="speaker-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          <div class="speaker-event">
            <p class="speaker-date">April 14, 2026</p>
            <p class="speaker-date">UXAWAY | Interview</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="deck-ui">
      <div class="progress-bar" id="progress"></div>
      <div class="bottom-cover"></div>
      <div class="top-meta">
        <div></div>
        <div class="page-title" id="pageTitle">Designing as an AI-First Designer</div>
      </div>

      <div class="nav" aria-label="Presentation navigation">
        <button class="nav-btn" id="prevBtn" type="button" aria-label="Previous slide">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M9.5 3.5L5 8l4.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>

        <div class="nav-dots" id="dots" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <button class="nav-btn" id="nextBtn" type="button" aria-label="Next slide">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M6.5 3.5L11 8l-4.5 4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="bottom-meta">
        <div class="brand">
          <img class="brand-mark" src="https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/c648e968-6e1c-4dc4-941c-b8d715fb3235" alt="UX Sweet logo">
          <div class="brand-label">UX Sweet</div>
        </div>

        <div class="count">
          <span id="currentSlide">1</span>
          <span>/</span>
          <span id="totalSlides">1</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const SLIDES = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(".slide"));
const TOTAL = SLIDES.length;
const progressEl = document.getElementById("progress");
const pageTitleEl = document.getElementById("pageTitle");
const currentSlideEl = document.getElementById("currentSlide");
const totalSlidesEl = document.getElementById("totalSlides");
const dotsEl = document.getElementById("dots");
const deckUiEl = document.querySelector(".deck-ui");
const prevBtn = document.getElementById("prevBtn");
const nextBtn = document.getElementById("nextBtn");
let currentIndex = 0;

function buildDots() {
  dotsEl.innerHTML = "";

  SLIDES.forEach((_, index) => {
    const dot = document.createElement("span");
    dot.className = "dot";
    dot.addEventListener("click", function () {
      goTo(index);
    });
    dotsEl.appendChild(dot);
  });
}

function updateControls() {
  const activeSlide = SLIDES[currentIndex];
  const title = activeSlide.dataset.title || "Presentation";
  pageTitleEl.textContent = title;
  deckUiEl.classList.toggle("ui-light-brand", activeSlide.classList.contains("light-ui"));
  currentSlideEl.textContent = String(currentIndex + 1);
  totalSlidesEl.textContent = String(TOTAL);
  progressEl.style.width = ((currentIndex + 1) / TOTAL * 100) + "%";

  Array.from(dotsEl.children).forEach(function (dot, index) {
    dot.classList.toggle("active", index === currentIndex);
  });

  const isSingleSlide = TOTAL <= 1;
  prevBtn.classList.toggle("is-disabled", isSingleSlide);
  nextBtn.classList.toggle("is-disabled", isSingleSlide);
  prevBtn.disabled = isSingleSlide;
  nextBtn.disabled = isSingleSlide;
}

function replayAnimations(slide) {
  slide.querySelectorAll(".a1,.a2,.a3,.a4,.a5,.af").forEach(function (el) {
    el.style.animation = "none";
    void el.offsetHeight;
    el.style.animation = "";
  });
}

function goTo(index) {
  SLIDES[currentIndex].classList.remove("active");
  currentIndex = (index + TOTAL) % TOTAL;
  SLIDES[currentIndex].classList.add("active");
  replayAnimations(SLIDES[currentIndex]);
  updateControls();
}

function scaleDeck() {
  const deck = document.getElementById("deck");
  const vw = window.innerWidth;
  const vh = window.innerHeight;
  const scale = Math.max(vw / 1920, vh / 1080);
  const offsetX = (vw - (1920 * scale)) / 2;
  const offsetY = (vh - (1080 * scale)) / 2;
  deck.style.transform = "translate(" + offsetX + "px," + offsetY + "px) scale(" + scale + ")";
}

buildDots();
updateControls();
prevBtn.addEventListener("click", function () {
  if (TOTAL > 1) {
    goTo(currentIndex - 1);
  }
});
nextBtn.addEventListener("click", function () {
  if (TOTAL > 1) {
    goTo(currentIndex + 1);
  }
});
document.addEventListener("keydown", function (event) {
  if (TOTAL <= 1) {
    return;
  }

  if (["ArrowRight", "ArrowDown", " "].includes(event.key)) {
    event.preventDefault();
    goTo(currentIndex + 1);
  }

  if (["ArrowLeft", "ArrowUp"].includes(event.key)) {
    event.preventDefault();
    goTo(currentIndex - 1);
  }
});
scaleDeck();
window.addEventListener("resize", scaleDeck);
</script>
</body>
</html>
